item.title: 99 Farming
item.description:
99 Farming
To anyone who came to this video from top viewed gaming videos: I never expected this to be a top viewed gaming video, and frankly I have no idea why it is. Even if you read this description, I wrote; "This video has no purpose and it sucks" it's a video I made only for personal progress purposes to remember when I got the skill to 99. It's a shame a commentary or a video of mine about this game that actually required time and editing wasn't on the top page. I'm only mad that people are assuming I wanted this to be﻿ a top video, you guys are the reason (haters) why this video keeps getting more views. Instead of hating and disliking, take the time to look at my page, and watch an "RSMV" or a "Commentary" from me, then you can collectively hate. Just give it a chance instead of immediately hating. 99 Farming I can now grow super potatoes. This video has no purpose and it sucks, I just uploaded it to remember when I got 99 Farming for progress purposes (Achieved on September 12th, 2011).
